name: com.android.managedprovisioning.preprovisioning.DownloadRoleHolderActivity
description: Spinner which takes care of network connectivity if needed, and downloading of the role holder. If successfully connected to network and downloaded the role holder, #RESULT_OK is returned. Otherwise the result is #RESULT_CANCELED. If the result is #RESULT_CANCELED, it may be accompanied by ErrorDialogUtils#EXTRA_DIALOG_TITLE_ID, ErrorDialogUtils#EXTRA_ERROR_MESSAGE_RES_ID and ErrorDialogUtils#EXTRA_FACTORY_RESET_REQUIRED which can be used to display in a user-visible dialog.
